---
import Whisk from './illustrations/Whisk.astro';
import MapPin from './illustrations/MapPin.astro';
---

<section id="about" class="relative py-24 md:py-40 px-6 md:px-12 bg-ivory texture-paper overflow-hidden" data-section="about">
  <!-- Whisk decoration -->
  <div class="absolute top-16 right-12 opacity-20 hidden md:block">
    <Whisk size="w-10 h-20" class="tilt-right" />
  </div>

  <div class="mb-16 md:mb-24">
    <span class="text-label text-sage">02 — Our Story</span>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 md:gap-20">
    <!-- Left: Polaroid photos -->
    <div class="w-full md:w-[40%] relative">
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="bg-white p-3 pb-12 rounded-sm shadow-lg tilt-left inline-block">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517433367423-c7e5b0f35086?w=600&auto=format&q=80"
            alt="Baker's hands kneading dough on a flour-dusted wooden surface"
            class="w-64 h-72 object-cover rounded-sm"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <p class="text-script text-base text-caramel/60 mt-2 text-center">morning bake</p>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-8 -right-4 md:right-8 bg-white p-3 pb-12 rounded-sm shadow-lg tilt-right inline-block">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509042239860-f550ce710b93?w=400&auto=format&q=80"
            alt="Fresh espresso being pulled into a small white cup"
            class="w-40 h-48 object-cover rounded-sm"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <p class="text-script text-sm text-caramel/60 mt-2 text-center">slow-pulled espresso</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: Editorial Copy -->
    <div class="w-full md:w-[55%] md:ml-auto flex flex-col justify-center">
      <h2 class="text-display-lg text-cocoa mb-10 md:mb-16">Our Story</h2>

      <div class="max-w-xl space-y-6">
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-espresso/80">
          <span class="font-display text-6xl md:text-7xl italic float-left mr-3 mt-1 leading-[0.8] text-caramel font-bold">B</span>akes
          Bay is Coimbatore's café, bakery and kitchen — all under one warm cream-coloured roof. We pull
          espresso the way we laminate croissants and the way we fold dough for pizza: slowly, by hand,
          and with the quiet belief that a little patience tastes different.
        </p>

        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-espresso/60">
          Four branches across Coimbatore now, and the menu has grown with us — from a single counter of
          faloodas to a full café serving wood-counter pizzas, Alfredo pastas, Chinese wok classics,
          morning bakes, cold brews, and cakes baked to order for every birthday and every Tuesday that
          deserves celebrating.
        </p>

        <blockquote class="border-l-3 border-caramel/40 pl-6 py-4 my-10">
          <p class="text-script text-2xl md:text-3xl text-cocoa leading-snug">
            "A café for the morning, a bakery for the counter, a kitchen for the evening —
            and a cake for whenever you need one."
          </p>
        </blockquote>

        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-espresso/60">
          What started as a small neighbourhood bake on Maruthamalai Road has become four corners of
          Coimbatore's café culture. The recipes stayed the same: made by hand, made fresh, made with
          intention.
        </p>

        <p class="text-script text-lg text-caramel mt-8">— The Bakes Bay Family</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Origin vignette -->
  <div class="origin-vignette mt-24 md:mt-32 max-w-5xl mx-auto border-t border-caramel/20 pt-16 md:pt-20">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-10 md:gap-16">
      <div class="shrink-0 flex items-center gap-4">
        <MapPin size="w-10 h-12" />
        <div>
          <p class="text-label text-caramel/60 mb-1">Where we bake</p>
          <p class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl italic font-semibold text-cocoa">Coimbatore</p>
          <p class="text-script text-lg text-caramel">four branches</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-espresso/70 max-w-xl">
        At the foot of the Western Ghats, our kitchens open before the city wakes. Flour dust
        catches the first light, the ovens warm the rooms, and by the time the hills come into view,
        the first trays are out — in all four of our corners.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
